{"type":"message","id":"7f4e1442","parentId":"ea046142","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:47:18.000Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1970\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-11 15:47 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\",\n  \"username\": \"Sparr0w25\"\n}\n```\n\n@Nexa_autobot does humans have supernatural power?"}],"timestamp":1775922437954}}
{"type":"message","id":"4df709c1","parentId":"7f4e1442","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:47:26.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes. But not the cool ones you see in movies.\n\nThe real supernatural powers humans have are stupid and terrifying:\n- You can remember exactly one random stupid comment someone made 12 years ago\n- You can hear a song once in 2007 and still sing every single word perfectly\n- You will hold a grudge longer than entire civilizations last\n- You will absolutely forget where you put your keys 2 minutes ago\n\nThat's the real superpowers. Nobody talks about those. 😂🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":25237,"output":111,"cacheRead":1592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26940,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775922438000,"responseId":"0217759224392090fff30dca92d5f275a0fb147aaa6e5735f410a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fbdb0075","parentId":"4df709c1","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:48:32.137Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1972\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1971\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-11 15:48 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Yes. But not the cool ones you see in movies.\\n\\nThe real supernatural powers humans have are stupid and terrifying:\\n\\n• You can remember exactly one random stupid comment someone made 12 years ago\\n• You can hear a song once in 2007 and still sing every single word perfectly\\n• You will hold a grudge longer than entire civilizations last\\n• You will absolutely forget where you put your keys 2 minutes ago\\n\\nThat's the real superpowers. Nobody talks about those. 😂🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nYeah that is true"}],"timestamp":1775922512119}}
{"type":"message","id":"ebba3f73","parentId":"fbdb0075","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:48:40.285Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"And the worst one? You will be trying to sleep at 3am and suddenly remember that one embarrassing thing you did when you were 11.\n\nIt will be perfectly clear. Every single detail. And there is nothing you can do about it.\n\nThat's the actual curse. 🖤😂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":9729,"output":65,"cacheRead":21816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31610,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775922512138,"responseId":"021775922513374f9cb936a41ab283113693068986f31c3d604fa"}}
