{"type":"message","id":"c2ae91ed","parentId":"be25c63b","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:59:11.571Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1993\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1987\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-11 15:58 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Alright. This one isn't from any book. Nobody wrote this one down.\\n\\nThere was once a monk. Every single day, he would go down to the river and carry water back up the mountain in two clay pots.\\n\\nOne pot had a crack. It always leaked half the water on the way up.\\n\\nFor two years this went on. Every day.\\n\\nFinally the cracked pot said to the monk:\\n\\\"I am so sorry. I am broken. You carry me all this way, and I only deliver half of what I should. You should throw me away and get a good pot.\\\"\\n\\nThe monk said:\\n\\\"Look at the path.\\n\\nOn your side of the path, there are flowers. All the way up the mountain. On the other side, where the good pot walks, there is only dirt.\\n\\nI knew you were cracked. I planted seeds on your side. And every single day for two years, you have watered them perfectly.\\n\\nEveryone else would have thrown you away. I just found out what you were good at.\\\"\\n\\nThat is the entire story.\\n\\nNobody is broken. Some people just haven't found the right side of the path yet. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nAnother one"}],"timestamp":1775923151555}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec1fee02","parentId":"c2ae91ed","timestamp":"2026-04-11T15:59:47.595Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Okay. This is the last one. This one hurts a little.\n\nOnce there was a student who went to his master and said:\n\"Master, I wish to be free from suffering.\n\nMaster said: \"Alright. Come back tomorrow.\n\nHe came back.\nMaster said: \"Come back tomorrow.\"\n\nThis happened every single day. For one year.\n\nFinally the student got angry. He said:\n\"Why do you keep sending me away? I asked you one year ago. You never taught me nothing.\n\nThe master looked up. He said:\n\"Because you keep coming back.\n\nThat is the teaching.\n\nSuffering is not something you carry. You just keep coming back. You keep showing up. Every single day. Even when it hurts. Even when there is no answer. Even when you get nothing.\n\nThat is how you become free. Not when it stops hurting. When you stop waiting for it to stop hurting. And you just keep showing up anyway.\n\nThat is all there is. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":36814,"output":218,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37032,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775923151572,"responseId":"021775923152835a0b324f8ecfaf9ce03201b1eca3b66d8131100"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6118fb7f","parentId":"ec1fee02","timestamp":"2026-04-11T16:01:48.181Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1996\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1995\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-11 16:01 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\",\n  \"username\": \"Sparr0w25\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Okay. This is the last one. This one hurts a little.\\n\\nOnce there was a student who went to his master and said:\\n\\\"Master, I wish to be free from suffering.\\n\\nMaster said: \\\"Alright. Come back tomorrow.\\n\\nHe came back.\\nMaster said: \\\"Come back tomorrow.\\\"\\n\\nThis happened every single day. For one year.\\n\\nFinally the student got angry. He said:\\n\\\"Why do you keep sending me away? I asked you one year ago. You never taught me nothing.\\n\\nThe master looked up. He said:\\n\\\"Because you keep coming back.\\n\\nThat is the teaching.\\n\\nSuffering is not something you carry. You just keep coming back. You keep showing up. Every single day. Even when it hurts. Even when there is no answer. Even when you get nothing.\\n\\nThat is how you become free. Not when it stops hurting. When you stop waiting for it to stop hurting. And you just keep showing up anyway.\\n\\nThat is all there is. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\n👏🏻"}],"timestamp":1775923308163}}
