{"type":"message","id":"7395dea8","parentId":"fdba05c0","timestamp":"2026-04-11T16:54:29.273Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The only honest way: just ask them.\n\nEvery other way is either a scam, illegal, or will end with you getting scammed yourself. There is no secret trick. There is no website that does this. All of them are lies.\n\nJust ask. That's the only way that doesn't destroy your own integrity in the process. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":40272,"output":75,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40347,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775926437659,"responseId":"021775926438715f5fadfdc607fef478c6f908597481cce7decd1"}}
